    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――現在、星見高校学園祭にて",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "昔のことですから、詳しくは覚えていないんですが\nその写真展は綺麗に飾り付けされていました",
      "startTime": 6.8000000477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "写真も丁寧に飾っていて……ありふれたものばかり\nでしたけど、その人が写ってる写真もあって",
      "startTime": 15.0666667144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか不思議と、こういう場所で青春を過ごせたら\nとっても楽しいんだろうなって思えたんです",
      "startTime": 23.233333381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……本当に素敵な思い出だな\n話してくれてありがとう",
      "startTime": 30.6000000079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "『麻奈の母校だから』、『学園祭でやった麻奈の\nライブを観たのがきっかけで』……",
      "startTime": 36.4333333413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういった理由で入学希望者は増えたらしいが\n渚のようなきっかけは初めて聞いたよ",
      "startTime": 41.6914841214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "私もライブに行けていたら\nきっかけが変わっていたかもしれませんね",
      "startTime": 46.7020646256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの話だと、麻奈のライブがあった年\nだったんだよな、観なかったのか？",
      "startTime": 52.5218741566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "整理券を配るくらい満員で、体育館に入れなくて……\n麻奈さんのライブ、生で観たかったなぁ",
      "startTime": 60.8594346525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "無理にでも観に行った方が良かったかな……\nなんて今も思っちゃうぐらいで……あれ？",
      "startTime": 68.3261013192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、あの写真展の中に麻奈さんの……\nあれ、待って……それなら同じクラスのはず……",
      "startTime": 79.1594346525,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 907.2320459000025,
          "startTime": 74.0666666746
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4340.565379200001,
          "startTime": 77.5000000079
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8440.565379199996,
          "startTime": 81.6000000079
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "でもかき氷屋さんって言ってたけど……\nうーん？　辻褄が合うようで合わないような……",
      "startTime": 88.93687346,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 907.2320458999883,
          "startTime": 85.6666666746
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3007.2320458999966,
          "startTime": 87.7666666746
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5107.232045899991,
          "startTime": 89.8666666746
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7340.565379199987,
          "startTime": 92.1000000079
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5405.758571600003,
          "startTime": 94.3426320316
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6763.1265479,
          "startTime": 95.7000000079
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8129.793214599999,
          "startTime": 97.0666666746
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "な、渚！　何か考え込んでるところ悪いが、スマホが\n何度も鳴ってるぞ。確認した方がいいんじゃないか",
      "startTime": 98.7333333413,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 98.3000000079
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　あれ、いつの間に……わわっ！？\n琴乃ちゃんからヘルプのメッセが大量に！？",
      "startTime": 106.7885051889,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3078.161509499992,
          "startTime": 105.1666666746
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません、{user}さん！\n私、戻ります！　お店とっても混んでるみたいで",
      "startTime": 112.2218385222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "最後まで案内出来ないのは名残惜しいですが……\n絶対後で、私達の猫耳メイド喫茶に来て下さいね！",
      "startTime": 120.3885051889,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4811.494811000003,
          "startTime": 125.1999999999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。……しかし写真展か。確か俺も、三年の頃に\nやったっけか。懐かしいな……あの時、あいつが――",
      "startTime": 132.8333307981,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4099.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 136.9333307981
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "おっと、今度は俺のスマホにメッセか\n渚からだな……は？　「気絶しそう」！？",
      "startTime": 141.8999974648,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5193.960523300007,
          "startTime": 143.0333307981
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "こ、この短時間で一体全体何があった！？\n今向かうぞ、渚！",
      "startTime": 150.0666641314,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4739.171481299991,
          "startTime": 151.4716712956
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "お帰りなさいませ、ご主人様～！\n猫耳メイドの渚が担当させていただきますね",
      "startTime": 157.5666641314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "元気そうで何よりだよ……気絶しそうだったのは\n奥で小さくなってる琴乃が原因か……",
      "startTime": 165.9666641314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "キッチン担当のはずの琴乃が猫耳メイド姿に……\nそうか、念願が叶ったんだな……",
      "startTime": 173.8333307981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！！　予想以上にお店が大人気で\n人手が足りなくなって、急遽お願いしました！",
      "startTime": 180.3999974648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり国宝級ですよね……本当に凄い\n見ているだけで意識が遠のいちゃうよ～……",
      "startTime": 189.0666641314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "はは……琴乃もだけど渚もよく似合っているよ\nやっぱりお店の中だと、一段と映えるな",
      "startTime": 198.7666641314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
